&lt;p&gt;Most of my life was spent in the business world, but my real interest was in the unexplained mysteries. I spent my spare time reading about aliens, UFOs and government cover-ups, but couldn’t get enough answers. So in 2013 when I got the opportunity to take over the Blue Planet Project and once again make this amazing, mysterious book available to the public, I jumped at it and dropped everything else I was involved in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anxious to share with my readers what I learned from exhaustive research, information from government insiders, psychics, and even those who actually are able to communicate with aliens on a regular basis.&lt;/p&gt;
